                "caption": "Figure 5:Performance evaluation and failure mode analysis.DP denotes Diffusion Policy, with -T and -C representing Transformer and CNN-based architectures, respectively.(a)Comparison of average success rates across different baselines under the “rand-obj” (Table2) condition.(b)and(c)provide a detailed breakdown of failure modes forπ0.5\\pi_{0.5}and DP-C. These statistics are aggregated from 550 evaluation trials (50 runs across 11 tasks) to identify main bottlenecks in dexterous manipulation.",
